title: Weingut Feuerwehr Wagner
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Organic, Buffet, Beer/Wine, Austrian, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Traditional Austrian food but with veggie choices like vegetable quiche, lentils loaf on salad, escalopes, rissoles, fried vegetable bags, a vegan version of the Viennese spread liptauer. Makes cakes and pastries. Menu changes constantly. Has vegan wine and desserts.
